      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PINK POPPY CLUB (5) has a strong record this track and trip including three wins from four starts. Scored by 0.8 lengths last time (19.96) in a TG1-4W over 342m at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. TIME OF DESIGN (2) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 4th and beaten 3 lengths at this track (20.24). Will give the top chances plenty to think about. ADHANA CARL (1) turned in a plain effort last time when sixth at Murray Bridge over 455m behind Brother Bilo (27.15) in a Grade 6. Was in the money prior to that. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Expected to feature in the finish. WHITE HOT DREAMS (4) placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.",
